= Scale: log-N curve

#figure-svg(
  "/target/gossip-bench/figures/scale_n.svg",
  [At #math.italic[f] = 3, sweeping cluster size N from 4 to 128.
   Left: observed rounds-to-converge against the #math.log_2 N
