// =====================================================================
// 9. Bandwidth scaling
// =====================================================================
= Bandwidth scaling (SWIM constant load)

The SWIM paper's headline structural property is that the gossip
component's per-node load stays constant as the cluster grows
(in their bench: #math.italic[T'] ticks of fixed-size payload per
node). The convergence suite already exercises N from 4 to 64; the
table below extracts the #math.italic[f] = 3 column.

